SUMMARY:Essex Escapade
DESCRIPTION:Metrotrails: NJ\, PA\, NY Metropolitan Area Hiking and More!\n
 Chaining together several lovely parks in Essex County for a 7-8 mile loop
  hike.\n\n**Highlights:**\n\n* **The Bonsal Preserve:** Seemingly\, nobody
  who doesn't live next to it knows it's there.\n* **Tuers Park**\n* **Yant
 acaw Brook Park**\n* **Brookdale Park\\***\n* **Watchung Park**\n* **Edgem
 ont Memorial Park**\n* **Anderson Park\\***\n* **Sunset Park**\n\n*\\*Thes
 e are **Olmsted** Parks\, designed by the same firm that designed NYC's Ce
 ntral Park.*
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/metrotrails/events/313597271/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260302T042621Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260302T042621Z
